<h5 id="subject_786132">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=83596.msg786132#msg786132" rel="nofollow">【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】车辆与无人机（vehicles and drones）  P.461-P.466</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_786132'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_786132'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2016-03-28, 周一 14:03:11 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_786132_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_786132"><strong>感谢jim老爷的校对，为翻译帮了大忙，辛苦了！<br>感谢dm马丁通过karma激励我翻译这段文字。<br></strong><br><br>车辆与无人机<br>Vehicals and drones<br>在P198页的Vehicles中已经定义了战斗中使用的车辆属性。车辆还有一项非战斗属性，座位，用来决定车适合搭载多少人（包括操作者），以及在紧要关头能够载货的空间多寡——每个座位可以用来容纳250千克的货物。座位（乘客用）可以在车内额外容纳150%的人，不过这样做会使车辆的速度和操控属性各减一。你可以在你的越野摩托后面多坐一个人，或者往轿车后排座椅上塞进超过安全数量的人，不过你的车不会表现得像往常那么好了。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Vehicle attributes used in combat are defined in Vehicles, <br>p. 198. Vehicles also have a non-combat attribute, Seating, which determines both how many people can fit in <br>the vehicle (including the operator) and also, in a pinch, <br>additional cargo space—one ‘seat’ can also be used to <br>hold up to 250 kilograms of cargo. Seating (for people) <br>can be exceeded by up to 150 percent by stuffing people <br>inside, but doing so decreases the vehicle’s Speed and <br>Handling attributes by one. So you can have that extra <br>person ride on the back of a dirtbike, or stuff a more-thansafe amount of people into the back of a sedan, but your <br>vehicle’s not going to provide quite its usual kick.</div></div></div><br>机械师界面（Rigger interface）：当机械师界面装在一辆车上时，它允许你使用控制装备来直接通过VR接入并控制这辆车。一个标准的机械师界面能够让一辆车被光纤电缆或者无线链接控制。详见Being the machine，p265。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Rigger interface: When added to a vehicle, this lets <br>you use a control rig to jump in and control it directly <br>through immersive virtual reality. The standard rigger <br>interface allows the vehicle to be controlled with either <br>a direct fiber-optic cable or wireless link. See Being the <br>Machine, p. 265</div></div></div><br>武器挂载位（Weapon mounts）：<br>车辆可以装备不超过其未扩展的体质/3（向下取整)的武器挂载位。标准武器挂载位能够装配任何突击步枪或更小规格的武器和250发的弹药。重武器挂载位算作两个武器挂载位，并且能够装配任何武器和500发的链式弹药或者不超过体质的火箭/导弹。所有武器挂载都可以远程操作而且可以瞄准并攻击90度角内的物体（水平和垂直）。可以增加手动操作，不过只能用于车辆，无人机则不行，而且需要额外的花费。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Weapon mounts: Vehicles may be equipped with a <br>number of weapon mounts equal to their unaugmented <br>Body ÷ 3 (round down). Standardweapon mounts may <br>hold any assault rifle or smaller-sized weapon and 250 <br>rounds of ammo. Heavyweapon mounts count as two <br>weapon mounts and can hold any weapon and up to<br>500 rounds of belted ammo or up to Body rockets/mis-<br>siles. All weapon mounts are operated remotely and can <br>target a ninety-degree arc of fire (horizontal and verti<br>cal). Manualoperation can be added, but only for vehi<br>cles, not drones, and at extra cost.</div></div></div><br>————————————————————————————————————————<br>车辆改造表格<br>车辆改装<br>改装&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;可用性&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;花费<br>机械师界面&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1,000¥<br>标准武器挂载位 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8F &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2,500¥<br>重型武器挂载位 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;14F &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5,000¥<br>手动操作&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+500¥<br>————————————————————————————————————————<br><br>机车（bikes）<br>操控机车需要陆用驾驶技能。许多机车都使用电能或混合生物燃料引擎。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &