: This cheap four-door sports<br>sedan is a fast, powerful car for corp youth to show off<br>their moxie to their friends in a socially acceptable and<br>constructive way. Available for low prices out of the box,<br>the Shin-Hyung is often heavily customized by tuners and<br>street racing enthusiasts to the point of being far more<br>functional and barely recognizable.The Shin-Hyung can<br>be bought cheap, goes fast, and handles well. What else<br>could you want? These facts have made it popular with<br>Triad and Yakuza elements as well as more affluent street<br>gangs and slumming rich-kids.</div></div></div><br>欧元卡西风3000（Eurocar Westwind 3000）：这款光滑，经典，低矮的速度机器将商务与娱乐完美的混合在了一起。定位在奢华和性能的交叉点，这辆装有涡轮增压变速器的跑车对于大部分在阴影中工作的炉渣们来说这是一个白日梦。它性感的线条和强劲的引擎使它在肌肉车爱好者中始终保持强力。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Eurocar Westwind 3000: This sleek, classic, low-slung<br>speed machine mixes business and pleasure into perfec<br>tion. Situated perfectly at the intersection of luxury and<br>performance, this is a turbo-charged sportscar that is only<br>a pipe dream for most slags working their way up through<br>the shadows. Its sexy lines and powerful engine make it<br>consistently powerful among muscle car enthusiasts.</div></div></div><br>福特·美利车（Ford Americar）：这辆四门轿车有一个令人担负得起的价格点，大容量行李箱和安全的功能，这些方面结合起来让他在近几十年来一直是北美最畅销的家庭车辆，直到它输给Mercury Comet为止。Americar即可靠又实惠，但是不快也不性感。如果你想将四个泛人类从A点运往B点，用一辆Ford Americar或许是最直截了当也最不引人注目的方式。它不闪亮也不时髦，但很多时候闪亮会要了你的命。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Ford Americar: This four-door sedan has an afford<br>able price point, capacious luggage storage, and safety <br>features that, combined, made it the bestselling family <br>car in North America for decades before losing out to the <br>Mercury Comet. The Americar is reliable and economical, <br>but not fast or sexy. If you need to ferry four metahumans <br>from point A to point B, a Ford Americar is probably the <br>most straightforward and anonymous way to do so. It’s <br>not flashy, and it’s not stylish, but sometimes flashy gets <br>you killed.</div></div></div><br>SK-宾利·协约者（Saeder-Krupp-Bentley Concordat）：这辆奢华的车时髦，庄重，令人印象深刻。它快速而有力，舒适又安全，内饰华贵，而且最重要的是，它是地位的象征。SK-Bentley Concordat是那种模星（simstars）和兽人腔饶舌歌手（orxploitation rapper）们开的车；一个坐在这车方向盘后面的狂奔者一定干得十分不错。或者，他们偷了一台。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Saeder-Krupp-Bentley Concordat: This luxury sedan <br>is stylish, stately, and impressive. It is fast and powerful, <br>comfortable and safe, opulently appointed, and most <br>importantly, a status symbol. The SK-Bentley Concordat <br>is the kind of car that simstars and orxploitation rappers <br>drive; a runner behind the wheel of one has made the big <br>time indeed. Either that, or they stole it.</div></div></div><br>三菱夜空（Mitsubishi Nightsky）：任性，安全，高科技，这辆武装的豪华轿车不是为你设计的。它为公司高官，影视明星，约翰逊先生而设计；只有与他们作伴的时候你才能有机会享受它宽敞的内部空间和奢华的设施。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Mitsubishi Nightsky: Decadent, secure, <br>and hightech, this armored limousine isn’t for <br>you. It’s for corp executives, media stars, and Mr. Johnson; only in their company will you enjoy its spacious interior and luxurious amenities.</div></div></div></div>
