ooking <br>for unexpected ways to approach nautical targets.</div></div></div><br>固定翼机<br>固定翼机需要空用驾驶技能。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">FIXED-WING AIRCRAFT<br>Fixed wing aircraft are operated with the Pilot Aircraft <br>skill.</div></div></div><br>阿尔忒弥斯工业夜鹰（Artemis Industries Nightwing）：Nightwing是一架老式超轻量级飞机，十分类似于那些二十世纪后期起源的飞机。Nightwing有被遮蔽的电动引擎用来使飞行器噪音最小化并减少热量排放——这样的目的是为了防止噪音污染和环境冲击，它的副作用使这个小型的类似滑翔机的飞行器变得十分隐秘。Nightwing在任何乡下航空爱好者，走私者，和其他任何喜欢典型潜行渗透的人中都十分流行。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Artemi