a的无人机的形状和外形都像大型昆虫，但能爬升的最大高度要高好多。它能起到“空中的眼睛”的作用，而且由于它难以被发现的特点，用来跟踪别人也十分便捷。这架无人机需要空用载具技能。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">MCT Fly-Spy: This Mitsuhama drone is the size and <br>shape of a large insect but can achieve substantially <br>better altitudes. It can serve in an “eye in the sky” role <br>and is handy for shadowing people given the fact that <br>t’s relatively hard to spot. This drone is operated with <br>the Pilot Aircraft skill.<br></div></div></div>小型无人机<br>SMALL DRONES<br><br>阿兹特克科技爬行者（Aztechnology Crawler）：这台小型的爬行者能够很轻松地处理楼梯和其他障碍。作为一款专门针对艰苦乡村和城市复杂地形而设计的远程刺探型无人机，Crawler既耐用又有效。它的驾驶程序比同等级的其他大部分无人机都要高级。这台无人机使用行走载具技能来操控。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Aztechnology Crawler: This small crawler can easily <br>handle stairs and other obstacles. Designed to operate <br>as a remote snooper in rough rural or urban terrain, the <br>Crawler is efficient and robust. Its Pilot program is a step <br>above most drones in its class. This drone is operated <br>with the Pilot Walker skill.</div></div></div><br>洛克希勒-眼睛-X2（Lockheed Optic-X2）:这架可以垂直和短距起降的隐秘无人机在折叠起来运输时，只有一台cyberdeck那么大。展开后的体积则与大型猎鹰或者其他类似的肉食鸟类相当。它特有的辐射限制技术使他成为了情报公司和狂奔者的宠儿；在使用雷达系统，视觉，听觉进行察觉检定尝试发现眼睛-X2时，需要受到-3骰池的惩罚。这架无人机使用空用载具技能。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Lockheed Optic-X2: This VSTOL stealth craft is only the <br>size of a cyberdeck with its wings folded up for transport. <br>When it is deployed, it is the size of a large hawk or oth<br>er bird of prey. Its patented signature-limiting technology <br>makes it a favorite of intelligence agencies and shadowrun<br>ners; radar systems and visual and audio Perception Tests <br>all receive a –3 dice pool penalty to spot the Optic-X2. This <br>drone is operated with the Pilot Aircraft skill.</div></div></div><br>中型无人机<br>MEDIUM DRONES<br><br>阿瑞斯决斗者（Ares Duelist）：这架中型，粗略拟人的步行无人机是个奇葩，或许有人会说它很新潮。它被设计成有双脚的巡逻者，就像一个泛人类安保守卫，并且配置了剑刃手臂作为天生武器。并且他的外形被设计成特殊的风格，外壳披着一种传统oyoroi武士甲，Renraku Red Samurai就穿这种护甲，也许是对某个竞争对手的暗讽。作为一款极少被部署于实战的作品，决斗者有两个明显的优点：拟人的外表令它在远距离上有可能被误认为多种泛人类守卫，这令它在保安人员有限的设施中十分有用。据说它的剑刃手臂在对抗精魂时比那些装备了除了枪还是枪的传统无人机更有用一些。这台无人机带有独一无二的三级瞄准（剑）的软件，并且在特殊武器挂载位带有一对标准剑刃。（挂载的剑不能够被其他武器替换，不过可以通过正常规则安装额外的武器挂载位。）这台无人机使用步行载具技能操纵。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Ares Duelist: This medium-sized, roughly anthro<br>morph walker drone is an oddity, some might say a nov<br>elty. It is designed to patrol on its two feet like a metahu<br>man security guard and is equipped with blade-arms as <br>its primary armaments. Furthermore, it has been stylized <br>so its outer chassis represents the traditional oyoroisamu<br>rai armor worn by the Renraku Red Samurai, perhaps a <br>subtle jab at a competing mega. A niche item that is sel<br>dom fielded, the duelist has two distinct advantages: its <br>humanoid profile allows it to be mistaken for a more-ver<br>satile metahuman guard at a distance, making it useful at <br>facilities guarded by skeleton crews, and its blade-arms <br>are allegedly marginally more effective at combating <br>spirits than the traditional drone combat payloads of guns <br>and more guns. This drone comes with a unique Rating <br>3 Targeting (Swords) autosoft and mounts a pair of stan<br>dard swords in special weapon mounts. (The mounted <br>swords cannot be replaced with other weapons, but addi<br>tional weapon mounts may be installed using the normal <br>rules.) This drone is operated with the Pilot Walker skill.<br></div></div></div>GM-尼桑 杜宾（GM-Nissan Doberman）：这台履带式大范围巡逻无人机能够十分有效地不分昼夜的保护指定的范围。它带有一个标准武器挂载位。这台无人机使用陆用载具驾驶。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">GM-Nissan Doberman: This tracked perimeter-pa<br>trol drone can secure its designated area effectively <br>during day or night conditions. It comes equipped with <br>a standard weapon mount. This drone is operated with <br>the Pilot Groundcraft skill.</div></div></div><br>MCT-尼桑 旋翼无人机：这是一架简单，实用的水平旋翼无人机，并且有着高度模块化和可自定义的设计。在决定它能够整合多少武器挂载位和自定义设计时，他的实际体质视为体质加3。这台无人机使用空用载具技能。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">MCT-Nissan Roto-Drone: The Roto-Drone is a sim<br>ple, no-nonsense rotor-wing drone design that is highly <br>modular and customizable. Treat its Body as 3 higher <br>than its actual Rating for determining how many weap<br>on mounts or customizations it can integrate. This drone <br>is operated with the Pilot Aircraft skill.</div></div></div><br>大型无人机<br>LARGE DRONES<br><br>赛博空间概念斑点狗（Cyberspace Designs Dalmatian）：这座耐用的大型垂直起降侦查无人机有空中悬停的功能，还有这对于它轻便的重量来说十分坚固的框架。它在储存时大概有割草机那么大，展开后则类似像一架大型悬挂式滑翔机。孤星和游侠公司都已获得授权在城市使用其进行巡逻和侦查的任务。斑点狗使用空用载具技能操纵。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Cyberspace Designs Dalmatian: This large and robust <br>VTOL recon drone is capable of hovering and has a sturdy <br>frame for its light weight. It is about the size of a lawn <br>mower when stored, and when deployed is the size of a <br>large hang glider. Lone Star and Knight Errant have both <br>licensed the design for urban surveillance and patrol du<br>ties. The Dalmatian is operated with the Pilot Aircraft skill.</div></div></div><br>钢铁山猫战斗无人机（Steel Lynx Combat Drone）：作为一台久经沙场的陆地战斗机器，钢铁山猫有四条配有轮子的腿和一个重型武器挂载位。它使用陆用载具技能进行操纵。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Steel Lynx Combat Drone: A hardened ground com<br>bat machine, the Steel Lynx possesses four wheeled <br>legs and a heavy weapon mount. It is operated with the <br>Pilot Groundcraft skill.</div></div></div><br><br>附：表格阅读注解<br>表格：<br>HANDL：操纵 Speed：速度 Accel：加速 Bod：体质 Armor：护甲 Pilot：驾驶员 Sensor：传感器 Seats：座椅 Avail：可用性 Cost：花费<br><br>表中的“*”代表车辆在公路上/不在公路上时候，车辆操纵和速度属性使用斜杠前/后的数值。</div>
